<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>纽约时报 &amp;gt; 美国 &amp;gt; 政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/spotlight/on-politics</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 15:01:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普和共和党人能收回有关经济的信息吗？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/15/us/politics/trump-taxes-economy-iran-war.html</link><description>今天是纳税日，但该国的大部分注意力都集中在一场不受欢迎的战争上。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 21:31:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/15/us/politics/trump-taxes-economy-iran-war.html</guid></item><item><title>埃里克·斯瓦尔韦尔下台后加州州长竞选会发生什么？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/13/us/politics/swalwell-california-governor.html</link><description>对于民主党人来说，这出戏的影响远远超出了州内范围。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 22:20:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/13/us/politics/swalwell-california-governor.html</guid></item><item><title>2028 年民主党可能候选人已经在争取黑人选民的支持</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/10/us/politics/black-voters-democrats-2028.html</link><description>可能的总统候选人已经在争取重要的民主党选区。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 21:32:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/10/us/politics/black-voters-democrats-2028.html</guid></item><item><title>谁为 2026 年中期选举提供资金？很多钱都无法追踪。</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/08/us/politics/midterms-elections-funding-pac.html</link><description>流入政治体系的大量资金最终无法追踪。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 22:21:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/08/us/politics/midterms-elections-funding-pac.html</guid></item><item><title>佛罗里达州的选区重划战争、佐治亚州的决选和最新的政治新闻</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/06/us/politics/redistricting-virginia-florida-ga-special-election-republicans.html</link><description>随着未来两周最后期限的临近，两者都没有完全按照党派计划进行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 21:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/06/us/politics/redistricting-virginia-florida-ga-special-election-republicans.html</guid></item><item><title>随着民主党在中期选举前变得乐观，六场参议院竞选值得关注</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/03/us/politics/senate-races-midterms-primary-election.html</link><description>对于该党来说，夺回控制权仍然是一项艰巨的任务。这是最新的。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 15:41:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/03/us/politics/senate-races-midterms-primary-election.html</guid></item><item><title>特朗普支持的路易斯安那州初选候选人也赞扬了 DEI。会伤害她吗？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/01/us/politics/julia-letlow-louisiana-republican-primary.html</link><description>路易斯安那州众议员朱莉娅·莱特洛 (Julia Letlow) 正在竞选挑战参议员比尔·卡西迪 (Bill Cassidy)，她因 2020 年的言论而面临保守派的反击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 21:39:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/01/us/politics/julia-letlow-louisiana-republican-primary.html</guid></item><item><title>缅因州、密歇根州及其他地区初选速成班</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/primary-elections-maine-michigan.html</link><description>这是关于接下来要发生的事情的速成课程。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 23:41:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/primary-elections-maine-michigan.html</guid></item><item><title>CPAC 考虑万斯、卢比奥和特朗普之后的生活</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/27/us/politics/cpac-trump-vance-rubio.html</link><description>一位与会者表示，总统的潜在继任者“都是凡人”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 21:53:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/27/us/politics/cpac-trump-vance-rubio.html</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的主要批评者、众议员托马斯·马西能在肯塔基州初选中坚持下去吗？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/us/politics/thomas-massie-trump.html</link><description>任何共和党人都可以不同意特朗普的观点并侥幸逃脱惩罚吗？托马斯·马西在肯塔基州的初选是一个关键考验。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 22:19:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/us/politics/thomas-massie-trump.html</guid></item></channel></rss>